SENIOR TWO
TERMI
TOPIC 2:
Soil
Duration: 36 Periods
General Objective:
By the end of the topic the learner should be able to understand the components of soil, their
contribution to the life of plants and animals and the necessity to conserve soil.

PERIOD SPECIFIC OBJECTIVE
CONTENT
•

formation,
composition
and profile

formed.

formation.

STRATEGIES

profile

constituents

functions.

2.2 Physical and
chemical
properties of
soil

properties of soil.

and water to plants and
animals.
Demonstrate porosity and

to plants and animals.

capacities of soils.

water retention, and
properties of soils.
